or these extraordinary things

00:12:54.850 --> 00:12:57.640 align:middle line:84%
happen to extraordinary
people, but I have

00:12:57.640 --> 00:12:59.450 align:middle line:90%
to tell you that is not true.

00:12:59.450 --> 00:13:01.300 align:middle line:84%
