the choice to become

00:13:01.300 --> 00:13:03.820 align:middle line:90%
spiritually unreasonable--

00:13:03.820 --> 00:13:05.650 align:middle line:90%
absolutely unreasonable.

00:13:05.650 --> 00:13:10.630 align:middle line:84%
It begins with a deep
journey into yourself.

00:13:10.630 --> 00:13:13.780 align:middle line:84%
This is a trick that I get
people to do in my workshop.

00:13:13.780 --> 00:13:16.150 align:middle line:84%
You need to get
to know yourself,

00:13:16.150 --> 00:13:19.040 align:middle line:84%
but in ways that
perhaps show you

00:13:19.040 --> 00:13:20.650 align:middle line:84%
something to make
you uncomfortable,

00:13:20.650 --> 00:13:22.000 align:middle line:90%
but it's a good uncomfortable.

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:23.440 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:13:23.440 --> 00:13:24.290 align:middle line:90%
You know what?

00:13:24.290 --> 00:13:30.510 align:middle line:84%
