rules you have about yourself.

00:13:30.510 --> 00:13:32.750 align:middle line:84%
So the first thing
you're going to do

00:13:32.750 --> 00:13:36.050 align:middle line:84%
is something that is
incredibly unreasonable.

00:13:36.050 --> 00:13:38.030 align:middle line:84%
