argument she engages in.

00:14:13.560 --> 00:14:15.860 align:middle line:10%
So one of the things
I do in my workshops

00:14:15.860 --> 00:14:19.370 align:middle line:10%
is I have people write
out their rule books.

00:14:19.370 --> 00:14:21.540 align:middle line:84%
