you to do your rulebook.

00:15:03.620 --> 00:15:06.920 align:middle line:84%
Because what I have people do
in my workshops is, once they

00:15:06.920 --> 00:15:11.390 align:middle line:84%
create their rulebook, I have
them introduce themselves

00:15:11.390 --> 00:15:14.540 align:middle line:84%
to someone they've never
met before, and hand over

00:15:14.540 --> 00:15:17.550 align:middle line:84%
the rulebook, and
say, hi, there.

00:15:17.550 --> 00:15:21.380 align:middle line:84%
