is Linda, or, my name is Tom,

00:15:21.380 --> 00:15:23.780 align:middle line:84%
and here are the rules
you need to know in order

00:15:23.780 --> 00:15:25.910 align:middle line:90%
to get to know me.

00:15:25.910 --> 00:15:32.730 align:middle line:84%
It is an experience of your
ego, and how frightened

00:15:32.730 --> 00:15:36.790 align:middle line:84%
