00:15:36.790 --> 00:15:41.670 align:middle line:84%
and what you will do to control
others before they control you.

00:15:41.670 --> 00:15:44.730 align:middle line:90%
It's a very humbling exercise.

00:15:44.730 --> 00:15:51.440 align:middle line:84%
It's a first step of getting
to know how afraid you

00:15:51.440 --> 00:15:52.880 align:middle line:90%
are of letting go.

00:15:52.880 --> 00:15:56.170 align:middle line:90%


00:15:56.170 --> 00:15:59.820 align:middle line:10%
This is about you
learning to defy gravity.

00:15:59.820 --> 00:16:01.210 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:16:01.210 --> 00:16:04.350 align:middle line:84%
Now, what do I mean
by defying gravity?

00:16:04.350 --> 00:16:07.680 align:middle line:84%
Gravity is
weightlessness, right?

00:16:07.680 --> 00:16:10.850 align:middle line:84%
But here's something
else about gravity.

00:16:10.850 --> 00:16:14.180 align:middle line:84%
Gravity, the root
of it is gravitas--

00:16:14.180 --> 00:16:17.390 align:middle line:90%
gravitas-- which is weight.

00:16:17.390 --> 00:16:21.350 align:middle line:84%
Now, you know what I learned
as a medical intuitive?

00:16:21.350 --> 00:16:25.730 align:middle line:84%
When you attach to
something energetically,

00:16:25.730 --> 00:16:27.380 align:middle line:90%
you give it weight.

00:16:27.380 --> 00:16:30.920 align:middle line:90%
You give it energetic weight.

00:16:30.920 --> 00:16:33.920 align:middle line:84%
And when you give
something weight--

00:16:33.920 --> 00:16:41.450 align:middle line:84%
W-E-I-G-H-T-- you actually
attach a relationship to time.

00:16:41.450 --> 00:16:47.060 align:middle line:84%
The more weight you give, the
longer you have to W-A-I-T

00:16:47.060 --> 00:16:48.140 align:middle line:90%
for everything.

00:16:48.140 --> 00:16:51.830 align:middle line:90%
So weight-- W-E-I-G-H-T--

00:16:51.830 --> 00:16:54.380 align:middle line:90%
equals an anchor.

00:16:54.380 --> 00:16:58.130 align:middle line:84%
So when you create
anchors for yourself,

00:16:58.130 --> 00:17:01.310 align:middle line:84%
you're literally creating
ways that are going

00:17:01.310 --> 00:17:03.110 align:middle line:90%
to take you to the grave--

00:17:03.110 --> 00:17:05.030 align:middle line:90%
gravitas.

00:17:05.030 --> 00:17:07.099 align:middle line:84%
And this is why Buddha
would always say,

00:17:07.099 --> 00:17:10.910 align:middle line:84%
you have to spot these illusions
and not attach yourself.

00:17:10.910 --> 00:17:13.040 align:middle line:84%
You're deciding, that
person broke my rules.

00:17:13.040 --> 00:17:15.380 align:middle line:84%
He said something,
she said something,

00:17:15.380 --> 00:17:19.010 align:middle line:84%
and I'm now deciding to
take that personally.

00:17:19.010 --> 00:17:22.640 align:middle line:84%
How many times in my life
I have gotten off a stage

00:17:22.640 --> 00:17:25.715 align:middle line:84%
after lecturing for hours,
and hours, and hours,

00:17:25.715 --> 00:17:29.580 align:middle line:84%
and I've been so tired,
and I've wanted to go back.

00:17:29.580 --> 00:17:31.800 align:middle line:84%
And someone has said,
could I just talked to you

00:17:31.800 --> 00:17:33.350 align:middle line:90%
for a moment?

00:17:33.350 --> 00:17:35.490 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, I
have been lecturing

00:17:35.490 --> 00:17:40.590 align:middle line:84%
for fruits 17,000 hours,
and I just want to go away.

00:17:40.590 --> 00:17:45.340 align:middle line:84%
And then I'd say, excuse me,
but I need to just leave here.

00:17:45.340 --> 00:17:48.760 align:middle line:10%
And they've taken my
exhaustion personally,

00:17:48.760 --> 00:17:52.480 align:middle line:10%
as if it had anything
to do with them.

00:17:52.480 --> 00:18:00.220 align:middle line:84%
Now, one of the things about
you beginning to lighten up

00:18:00.220 --> 00:18:09.700 align:middle line:84%
and becoming a free-floating
field is that you decide,

00:18:09.700 --> 00:18:11.920 align:middle line:90%
this is not a personal universe.

00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:15.340 align:middle line:90%
It's an impersonal universe.

00:18:15.340 --> 00:18:19.470 align:middle line:84%
I have to stop taking
things personally.

00:18:19.470 --> 00:18:20.700 align:middle line:90%
Think of Job.

00:18:20.700 --> 00:18:24.150 align:middle line:84%
This universe was not
created personally.

00:18:24.150 --> 00:18:27.540 align:middle line:84%
Nothing could be more
irrational a thought than

00:18:27.540 --> 00:18:31.128 align:middle line:84%
to think this universe
was created for me.

00:18:31.128 --> 00:18:33.470 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

