00:20:00.950 --> 00:20:06.290 align:middle line:10%
the universe in a way that
allows you to see grace

00:20:06.290 --> 00:20:11.360 align:middle line:10%
in action in a universe that
is both totally impersonal

00:20:11.360 --> 00:20:14.450 align:middle line:10%
and personal simultaneously--

00:20:14.450 --> 00:20:18.200 align:middle line:10%
that it is a place
where the ordinary

00:20:18.200 --> 00:20:22.340 align:middle line:10%
