the spiritually, how do I say,

00:20:36.340 --> 00:20:37.870 align:middle line:90%
amateurs--

00:20:37.870 --> 00:20:43.850 align:middle line:84%
for people who don't
get how God works.

00:20:43.850 --> 00:20:46.010 align:middle line:10%
If you think of
miracles as ordinary,

00:20:46.010 --> 00:20:47.780 align:middle line:10%
then they're not miracles.

00:20:47.780 --> 00:20:52.970 align:middle line:84%
They're just the nature
of God in everyday action

00:20:52.970 --> 00:20:58.100 align:middle line:84%
in a world that
functions on faith.

00:20:58.100 --> 00:21:01.440 align:middle line:84%
Now, think about your
world functioning that way.

00:21:01.440 --> 00:21:05.270 align:middle line:84%
And this is what I'm
going to suggest you try.

00:21:05.270 --> 00:21:07.130 align:middle line:84%
My suggestions for
people is that they

00:21:07.130 --> 00:21:10.070 align:middle line:84%
detach from their
preexisting image

00:21:10.070 --> 00:21:13.320 align:middle line:90%
of God as a off-planet man.

00:21:13.320 --> 00:21:16.120 align:middle line:90%
We've anthropomorphized god.

00:21:16.120 --> 00:21:19.730 align:middle line:84%
And while I can't explain
it in full measure,

00:21:19.730 --> 00:21:22.280 align:middle line:84%
I could snap my
fingers and say, I

00:21:22.280 --> 00:21:24.242 align:middle line:84%
want you to look
up in the heavens

00:21:24.242 --> 00:21:25.700 align:middle line:84%
and see what's
happening is there's

00:21:25.700 --> 00:21:28.227 align:middle line:84%
a collision of the
gods going on--

00:21:28.227 --> 00:21:29.510 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:21:29.510 --> 00:21:31.130 align:middle line:90%
--of all the Abrahamic gods--

00:21:31.130 --> 00:21:33.380 align:middle line:84%
of Judaism,
