in the heavens right now--

00:21:36.300 --> 00:21:38.050 align:middle line:90%
[KABOOM]

00:21:38.050 --> 00:21:44.860 align:middle line:84%
--because the heaven is
closing down the holy man

00:21:44.860 --> 00:21:47.080 align:middle line:90%
God archetype.

00:21:47.080 --> 00:21:50.170 align:middle line:84%
It's served us, but
now we're moving

00:21:50.170 --> 00:21:53.920 align:middle line:84%
into the era of
galactic theology.

00:21:53.920 --> 00:21:56.650 align:middle line:84%
Even now, as, I'm
talking to you in Rome

00:21:56.650 --> 00:21:58.510 align:middle line:84%
there's a gathering
of theologians,

00:21:58.510 --> 00:22:01.570 align:middle line:84%
and astrophysicists, and
astrobiologists trying

00:22:01.570 --> 00:22:05.440 align:middle line:90%
to script a galactic theology--

00:22:05.440 --> 00:22:09.370 align:middle line:84%
a God that is larger than
our image of ourselves

00:22:09.370 --> 00:22:11.980 align:middle line:90%
on this planet.

00:22:11.980 --> 00:22:15.430 align:middle line:84%
Give up the need to know why
things happen as they do.

00:22:15.430 --> 00:22:19.020 align:middle line:84%
Start being spiritually
irrational--

00:22:19.020 --> 00:22:20.500 align:middle line:90%
irrational.

00:22:20.500 --> 00:22:23.260 align:middle line:84%
Instead of saying, tell
me why this happened,

00:22:23.260 --> 00:22:27.520 align:middle line:84%
remind yourself that you're a
grain of sand in a huge ocean,

00:22:27.520 --> 00:22:30.400 align:middle line:84%
and just say, help
me learn from this.

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:32.320 align:middle line:84%
Connect with
meaning and purpose.

00:22:32.320 --> 00:22:35.320 align:middle line:84%
Don't expect meaning and purpose
to be delivered to your door

00:22:35.320 --> 00:22:37.570 align:middle line:84%
because it doesn't
happen that way.

00:22:37.570 --> 00:22:41.860 align:middle line:84%
You bring meaning and
purpose to everything.

00:22:41.860 --> 00:22:43.660 align:middle line:90%
Every word is power.

00:22:43.660 --> 00:22:45.610 align:middle line:90%
Words are power.

00:22:45.610 --> 00:22:49.870 align:middle line:84%
Watch how you frame
your universe.

00:22:49.870 --> 00:22:53.630 align:middle line:84%
And don't pray like
an ordinary mortal.

00:22:53.630 --> 00:22:56.330 align:middle line:84%
Prayers are not meant to
be petitions like you're

00:22:56.330 --> 00:22:57.300 align:middle line:90%
talking to Santa Claus.

00:22:57.300 --> 00:22:58.100 align:middle line:90%
Can I have?

00:22:58.100 --> 00:22:59.660 align:middle line:90%
Can I have more stuff?

00:22:59.660 --> 00:23:03.420 align:middle line:90%
Don't pray like a stuffologist.

00:23:03.420 --> 00:23:08.820 align:middle line:84%
Pray like you have
respect for the sacred.

00:23:08.820 --> 00:23:11.130 align:middle line:90%
And you pray with your soul.

00:23:11.130 --> 00:23:14.480 align:middle line:10%
Open me up.

00:23:14.480 --> 00:23:15.490 align:middle line:10%
Open me up.

00:23:15.490 --> 00:23:18.940 align:middle line:10%
Take me down deep, and
show me the reasons

00:23:18.940 --> 00:23:24.990 align:middle line:10%
you gave me this life, and give
me the candle on the night.

00:23:24.990 --> 00:23:26.490 align:middle line:90%
You're going to suffer.

00:23:26.490 --> 00:23:28.840 align:middle line:90%
That's life.

00:23:28.840 --> 00:23:32.810 align:middle line:84%
And you pray that you have the
courage not to betray people,

00:23:32.810 --> 00:23:34.190 align:middle line:90%
in yourself.

00:23:34.190 --> 00:23:36.140 align:middle line:90%
Make me courageous.

00:23:36.140 --> 00:23:37.760 align:middle line:90%
Make me integrous.

